  "notes": "Reconstructed Proto-Dravidian (c. 3000–2000 BCE, before IA arrival). Following Krishnamurti (2003): 5 vowel qualities × short/long; two stop series (initial: unaspirated; medial: voiced allophones); no aspiration contrast in native vocabulary; retroflex series (ʈ ɖ ɳ ɭ ɻ) — may be the source of IA retroflexes.",
